关系。瑙塞达的顾问早在去年12月20日澄清，总统并未参加开设“台湾代表处”的讨论。 然而据LRT消息，立陶宛外长兰茨贝尔吉斯（Gabrielius Landsbergis）1月5日反驳称，在开设“台湾驻立陶宛代表处”之前，他同总统瑙塞达协商了所有的步骤。 兰茨贝尔吉斯说：“在开设该代表处之前，我们不仅同总统讨论了所有事情，所有的步骤也都进行了协商。我不想再讨论这个问题了，因为正如我们所看到的，一些国内政策的细节很快就会转移到我们的外交政策上，无论我还是总统都不希望那样。”"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ih/X9g/2AkosKEAMaCDc1NjQ5MzYzIPif2o4GMCU4zARAIXIJNTEwMTU2MDYzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"61 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-30f4f623be7840acc748320c1e7b7261_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"34_1659844045.285801","card_id":"Q_546409182","target":{"id":546409182,"title":"生命重要还是钱重要？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/546409182","type":"question","created":1659341088,"answer_count":62,"follower_count":64,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[634,3489],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我们忙忙碌碌到底为了什么我们忙忙碌碌到底为了什么"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ih/X9g/2AkosKEAMaCDgzNzA3NDMzIKCSnpcGMAA4QEAicgk1NDY0MDkxODJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"35_1659844045.2861993","card_id":"Q_545796942","target":{"id":545796942,"title":"你们的高中生活都是咋样的呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/545796942","type":"question","created":1659001232,"answer_count":155,"follower_count":154,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[40546],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ih/X9g/2AkosKEAMaCDgzNTcxMjcwIJCziZcGMAA4mgFAI3IJNTQ1Nzk2OTQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","i